data.description: Welcome to Livonia's Beatrice Gardens~LOCATION is everything~ Capture your dream home with today's $10k reduction~ This Solid Brick Ranch is move-in ready ~ Start your new year with cozy fires in your open-concept kitchen/dining/family room ~ Lots of light in the large formal living room overlooking this quarter-acre lot~ Lots of remodeling completed and major updates like the beautiful brick foyer~ flooring, neutral paint, exterior vinyl siding, & refinished main bath too~Side entry driveway with attached oversized gargage~ mature trees and nice landscape~ "marry the house, date the rate" and come home today.
